Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-most-promising-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Einto%20the%20process%20to%20help%20companies%20save%C2%A0time%20and%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%2C%20Cavela%2C%20launched%20from%20stealth%20today%20with%20%242%20million%20in%20seed%20funding%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20learned.%20Early-stage%20VC%20firm%20XYZ%20Ventures%20led%20the%20funding%20round.%20Propel%20Ventures%20and%20Go%20Global%20Ventures%20also%20participated%20in%20the%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20company%20needs%20to%20find%20a%20supplier%2C%20it%20can%20take%20hundreds%20of%20messages%20%E2%80%94%20often%20in%20multiple%20languages%20across%20emails%2C%20WhatsApp%20messages%2C%20and%20texts%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20from%20concept%20to%20finished%20product.%20The%20process%20becomes%20even%20more%20time-consuming%20as%20companies%20speak%20with%20multiple%20suppliers%20in%20order%20to%20find%20the%20best%20partner%20to%20complete%20a%20specific%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20tall%20order%2C%20especially%20for%20small-%20and%20medium-sized%20businesses%20that%20don't%20have%20large%2C%20international%20procurement%20teams%2C%20explained%20Anthony%20Sardain%2C%20Cavela's%20CEO%20and%20founder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20his%20startup%20comes%20in%3A%20Cavela%20pairs%20companies%20with%20an%20AI%20agent%20that%20learns%20about%20the%20type%20of%20product%20they%20want%20to%20have%20manufactured.%20The%20agent%20then%20sources%20the%20products%20and%20negotiates%20with%20suppliers.%20All%20communication%20is%20managed%20on%20a%20central%20platform%2C%20which%20is%20easier%20to%20track%20than%20multiple%20email%20chains%20and%20text%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSourcing%20involves%20written%20communication%2C%20which%20can%20get%20really%20messy%2C%26quot%3B%20Sardain%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BLarge%20language%20models%20allow%20us%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20messiness%20of%20human%20language%20and%20improve%20an%20otherwise%20manual%2C%20involved%2C%20and%20convoluted%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESardain's%20family%20works%20in%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20he%20grew%20up%20living%20in%20multiple%20manufacturing%20hubs%20across%20Asia%20and%20Latin%20America%2C%20including%20Malaysia%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20Thailand%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20for%20Cavela%20when%20he%20was%20tasked%20with%20helping%20a%20family%20member%20source%20custom%20products%20for%20a%20hotel.%20The%20task%20was%20%26quot%3Btedious%20and%20time%20consuming%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20he%20put%20his%20tech%20and%20startup%20skills%20to%20use%20%E2%80%94%20Sardain%20is%20a%20data%20scientist%20by%20training%20and%20previously%20worked%20for%20Tierra%2C%20which%20maps%20and%20predicts%20crime%20in%20Latin%20America%20%E2%80%94%20to%20build%20a%20tool%20that%20could%20automate%20tasks%20and%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20a%20family%20background%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20business%2C%20Sardain%20said%20he's%20attuned%20to%20the%20challenges%20of%20global%20procurement%20%E2%80%94%20namely%2C%20the%20language%20barriers%20of%20working%20with%20suppliers%20in%20different%20countries%20and%20time%20zones.%20Rather%20than%20running%20an%20email%20through%20Google%20Translate%20and%20hoping%20for%20the%20best%2C%20Cavela's%20AI%20agents%20translate%20messages%20and%20communicate%20with%20suppliers%20and%20buyers%20in%20their%20time%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESardain%2C%20who%20now%20lives%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20says%20the%20end%20result%20is%20a%20better%20experience%20that%20takes%20less%20time%20and%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20saving%20businesses%20100s%20of%20hours%2C%20and%20there%20are%20brands%20that%20we've%20worked%20with%20that%20have%20cut%20production%20costs%20by%2040%25%20while%20ending%20up%20with%20an%20improved%20final%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManufacturing%20is%20at%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20for%20AI-driven%20innovation%20as%20the%20industry%20faces%20increasing%20demand%20for%20efficiency%2C%20scalability%2C%20and%20personalization.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20startups%20have%20capitalized%20on%20this%20shift%20to%20transform%20slices%20of%20the%20sector%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvcs-like-khosla-and-a16z-backing-robotics-that-use-ai-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20robotics%20space%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brightmachines.com%2Fnews%2Fbright-machines-raises-126m-series-c-funding-to-propel-manufacturing-into-software-defined-era%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBright%20Machines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20raised%20a%20%24126%20million%20Series%20C%20this%20summer%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcovariant.ai%2Fcovariant-adds-75m-in-series-c-funds-to-meet-customer-demand-for-scaled-ai-robotics-deployments%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECovariant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20closed%20a%20%2440%20million%20Series%20B%20in%20the%20spring%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcovariant.ai%2Fcovariant-adds-75m-in-series-c-funds-to-meet-customer-demand-for-scaled-ai-robotics-deployments%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstrumental%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20landed%20%2450%20million%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Cavela%2C%20the%20startup%20closed%20its%20%242%20million%20seed%20round%20without%20using%20a%20traditional%20pitch%20deck.%20Instead%2C%20the%20startup%20showed%20a%20video%20demonstration%20of%20the%20product%20that%20resonated%20with%20investors%2C%20Sardain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShopify%20solved%20one%20half%20of%20the%20equation%2C%20where%20it%20was%20very%20easy%20to%20sell%20things%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20remained%20was%20extremely%20high%20friction%3A