%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EImagine%20for%20a%20moment%20that%20you're%20a%20venture-capital%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20spot%20an%20entrepreneur%20who%20built%20a%20massive%20audience%20on%20social%20media%20by%20posting%20attention-grabbing%20content%20after%20studying%20algorithms%20and%20trends.%20They've%20started%20making%20lots%20of%20money%20from%20advertising%20and%20brand%20deals.%20They're%20even%20experimenting%20with%20launching%20their%20own%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESounds%20like%20YouTube's%20top%20creator%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-celebrity-cameos-mark-cuban-justin-timberlake-strategy-impact-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMrBeast%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Jimmy%20Donaldson)%2C%20right%3F%20It%20also%20sounds%20a%20bit%20like%20BuzzFeed%20cofounder%20Jonah%20Peretti%2C%20says%20Sam%20Lessin%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20the%20VC%20firm%20Slow%20Ventures.%20In%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Flessin%2Fstatus%2F1833545048543375856%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%2C%20the%20investor%20said%20MrBeast's%20growth%20story%20closely%20mirrored%20that%20of%20BuzzFeed%2C%20which%20also%20cracked%20the%20code%20of%20social-media%20virality%20but%20ultimately%20fizzled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20literally%20the%20same%20story%20all%20over%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Lessin%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20do%20MrBeast%20and%20early%20BuzzFeed%20have%20in%20common%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20built%20large%20followings%20on%20social%20media%20by%20posting%20viral%2C%20general-interest%20content%2C%20Lessin%20said.%20Both%20are%20reliant%20on%20platforms%20to%20reach%20their%20audiences%2C%20which%20can%20tweak%20their%20algorithms%20on%20a%20whim.%20And%20both%20post%20content%20that%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-on-why-his-copycats-wont-succeed-jimmy-donaldson-youtube-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelatively%20easy%20to%20imitate%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20attracts%20a%20broad%20audience%20instead%20of%20a%20niche%20community%20of%20fans%2C%20he%20said.%20That%20combination%20can%20be%20tough%20to%20monetize%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuzzfeed-varun-gupta-bill-pulte-vivek-ramaswamy-jonah-peretti-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuzzFeed%20has%20learned%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Its%20stock%20price%20is%20currently%20trading%20around%2090%25%20below%20its%202021%20public%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBuzzFeed%20was%20wrong%20to%20believe%20that%20you%20could%20growth%20hack%20your%20way%20to%20a%20valuable%20audience%2C%20and%20that%20audience%2C%20if%20it%20was%20really%20big%2C%20would%20be%20really%20valuable%2C%26quot%3B%20Lessin%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20really%20broad%20and%20big%2C%20but%20not%20specific%20and%20high%20spend%2C%20it's%20not%20valuable%2C%20which%20is%20partially%20what%20has%20collapsed%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELessin%20argued%20that%20for%20creators%20to%20build%20a%20lasting%20business%2C%20they%20need%20to%20specialize%20in%20a%20particular%20content%20vertical%2C%20attract%20a%20dedicated%20audience%20of%20fans%2C%20and%20then%20leverage%20their%20platform%20to%20sell%20an%20outside%20product%20or%20service%20that%20generates%20meaningful%20revenue.%20That%20type%20of%20more%20niche%20creator%20is%20exactly%20who%20Slow%20Ventures%20is%20targeting%20as%20part%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fslow-ventures-set-aside-20-million-invest-in-influencers-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreator%20equity%20investment%20program%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMedia%20is%20great%2C%20but%20candidly%2C%20from%20a%20venture-capital%20perspective%2C%20it%20just%20doesn't%20provide%20the%20return%2C%26quot%3B%20Lessin%20said.%20%26quot%3BMedia%20is%20an%20input%20to%20t