com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fkaty-perry-and-orlando-bloom-steal-the-show-with-sizzling-kiss-at-mtv-vmas-see-viral-photos%2Farticleshow%2F113293644.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113293644.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAt%20the%202024%20MTV%20VMAs%2C%20Katy%20Perry%20and%20Orlando%20Bloom%20stole%20the%20spotlight%20with%20their%20public%20display%20of%20affection.%20Bloom%E2%80%99s%20heartfelt%20introduction%20praised%20Perry%20as%20both%20a%20global%20star%20and%20a%20devoted%20partner.%20In%20her%20speech%2C%20Perry%20playfully%20thanked%20Bloom%20for%20his%20support%20and%20household%20help%2C%20reflecting%20her%20%26quot%3BQueen%20of%20Camp%26quot%3B%20persona.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fkaty-perry-and-orlando-bloom-steal-the-show-with-sizzling-kiss-at-mtv-vmas-see-viral-photos%2Farticleshow%2F113293644.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sitaram%20Yechury%20-%20%26quot%3BUnrepentant%20Marxist%26quot%3B%2C%20Author%20and%20Editor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20CPIM%20lost%20one%20of%20its%20staunchest%20pillars%20today%20as%20Sitaram%20Yechury%2C%20the%20party's%20three-time%20general%20secretary%2C%20strategist%2C%20think%20tank%2C%20author%20and%20editor%20of%20its%20mouthpiece%20People's%20Democracy%20for%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2072%20today.%20The%20veteran%20leader%20had%20been%20ailing%20for%20some%20time%20and%20was%20admitted%20at%20Delhi's%20All-India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20or%20AIIMS.%20He%20was%20being%20treated%20for%20acute%20respiratory%20tract%20infection%20and%20was%20on%20respiratory%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20five%20decades%2C%20Yechury%2C%20a%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Bengal%2C%20left%20his%20imprint%20not%20just%20on%20the%20CPM%20but%20also%20the%20national%20political%20canvas%20---%20playing%20an%20active%20role%20in%20drawing%20up%20the%20Common%20Minimum%20Programme%20for%20the%20United%20Front%20government%20in%201996.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20upholding%20party%20ideology%2C%20he%20was%20also%20seen%20as%20its%20pragmatic%20face%2C%20becoming%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20the%20coalition-building%20during%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20government%20in%202004%20--%20a%20role%20for%20which%20he%20was%20regarded%20as%20the%20bearer%20of%20the%20legacy%20of%20veteran%20party%20leader%20Harkishan%20Singh%20Surjeet.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20CPM's%20key%20interlocutor%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20despite%20the%20two%20parties%20being%20at%20loggerheads%20in%20Kerala%20and%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20days%2C%20he%20voiced%20the%20party's%20bitter%20opposition%20to%20the%20right%20wing%2C%20and%20emerged%20as%20a%20collaborative%20force%20within%20the%20Opposition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYechury's%20association%20with%20Leftist%20thoughts%20go%20back%20to%20his%20student%20days%20in%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20where%20he%20was%20doing%20his%20Masters'%20degree%20in%20Economics.%20Along%20with%20the%20other%20key%20CPM%20leader%20Prakash%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnKarat%2C%20he%20built%20up%20the%20formidable%20Left%20bastion%20in%20JNU%20that%20still%20endures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201975%2C%20he%20was%20jailed%20for%20organising%20resistance%20to%20the%20Emergency.%20Part%20of%20the%20CPM%20students'%20wing%20Students'%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20he%20was%20elected%20thrice%20to%20head%20it.%20A%20holder%20of%20a%20politburo%20seat%20for%2032%20years%2C%20he%20had%20succeeded%20Prakash%20Karat%20as%20the%20party%20general%20secretary%20in%202015%20and%20was%20elected%20for%20three%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20following%20years%2C%20Yechury%2C%20though%2C%20had%20differed%20with%20this%20oldest%20colleague%20on%20several%20key%20issues%20-%20the%20most%20prominent%20among%20them%20being%20part%20of%20the%20coalition%20in%201996%20and%20the%20Indo-US%20nuclear%20deal%20in%202008.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20he%20had%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20CPM%20forming%20a%20multi-party%20coalition%20with%20former%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Jyoti%20Basu%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20But%20the%20motion%20was%20defeated%2C%20with%20the%20opponent%20group%20being%20led%20by%20Prakash%20Karat%20and%20the%20United%20Front%20government%20led%20by%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda%20came%20to%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Indo-US%20nuclear%20deal%20too%2C%20the%20CPM%20Central%20Committee%20had%20rejected%20a%20proposal%20from%20Yechury%20that%20listed%20all%20the%20party's%20objections%20with%20which%20the%20Congress%20was%20on%20board.%20The%20party%2C%20instead%2C%20went%20along%20with%20Prakash%20Karat's%20suggestion%20to%20pull%20out%20support%20to%20the%20UPA%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Central%20leader%20of%20the%20CPM%20tasked%20with%20reviving%20the%20party%20in%20Bengal%20and%20Kerala%2C%20he%20had%20accepted%20it%20as%20a%20challenge%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20party's%20numbers%20in%20the%20parliament%20were%20ebbing.%20While%20he%20could%20not%20bring%20about%20an%20immediate%20resurgence%2C%20his%20ties%20with%20the%20state%20leaders%20remained%20close.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ailing%20leader%20had%20last%20uploaded%20a%20video%20on%20August%2022%20--%20days%20after%20he%20was%20hospitalised%20--%20a%20condolence%20message%20after%20the%20death%20of%20former%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Buddhadeb%20Bhattacharjee.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20my%20loss%20that%20I%20was%20not%20able%20to%20physically%20attend%20this%20memorial%20meeting%20and%20pay%20my%20homage%20to%20Com.%20Buddhadev%20Bhattacharya%26quot%3B%2C%20read%20the%20caption%20of%20his%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitaram%20Yechury%20is%20mourned%20by%20leaders%20across%20the%20political%20divide%20--%20a%20mark%20of%20his%20ability%20to%20keep%20personal%20connections%20despite%20political%20differences%2C%20and%20had%20friends%20even%20in%20the%20BJP%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BPained%20by%20the%20passing%20away%20of%20CPI(M)%20General%20Secretary%20and%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Shri%20Sitaram%20Yechuri.%20In%20his%20long%20years%20in%20public%20life%2C%20he%20distinguished%20himself%20as%20a%20seasoned%20parliamentarian%20who%20was%20known%20for%20his%20knowledge%20and%20articulation.%20He%20was%20also%20my%20friend%20with%20whom%20I%20had%20several%20interactions.%20I%20will%20always%20recall%20my%20interactions%20with%20him.%20Condolences%20to%20his%20bereaved%20family%20and%20supporters.%20Om%20Shanti!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20message%2C%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20spoke%20of%20their%20three-decade%20association%20and%20frequent%20collaborations.%20%26quot%3BSitaram%20Yechury%20-%20a%20very%20fine%20human%20being%2C%20a%20multilingual%20bibliophile%2C%20an%20unrepentant%20Marxist%20with%20a%20pragmatic%20streak%2C%20a%20pillar%20of%20the%20CPM%2C%20and%20a%20superb%20Parliamentarian%20with%20a%20wonderful%20wit%20and%20sense%20of%20humour%20-%20is%20most%20sadly%20no%20more.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20association%20stretched%20over%20three%20decades%2C%20and%20we%20collaborated%20closely%20at%20different%20occasions.%20He%20had%20friends%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%20and%20was%20admired%20for%20the%20strength%20of%20his%20convictions%20and%20for%20his%20most%20engaging%20personality%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20years%2C%20he%20had%20developed%20a%20close%20association%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20had%20jocularly%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Yechury)%20is%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20CPM%20and%20of%20the%20Congress%20too.%20And%20sometimes%20his%20influence%20in%20the%20Congress%20is%20more%20than%20in%20the%20CPM.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20condolence%20message%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSitaram%20Yechury%20ji%20was%20a%20friend.%20A%20protector%20of%20the%20Idea%20of%20India%20with%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20our%20country.%20I%20will%20miss%20the%20long%20discussions%20we%20used%20to%20have.%20My%20sincere%20condolences%20to%20his%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20followers%20in%20this%20hour%20of%20grief%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726143360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fpdhohd8o_sitaram-yechury-_650x400_12_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsitaram-yechury-unrepentant-marxist-author-and-editor-6548979%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CPIM%20lost%20one%20of%20its%20pillars%20today%20as%20Sitaram%20Yechury%2C%20the%20party's%20three-time%20general%20secretary%2C%20strategist%2C%20think%20tank%2C%20author%20and%20editor%20of%20its%20mouthpiece%20People's%20Democracy%2C%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2072.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsitaram-yechury-unrepentant-marxist-author-and-editor-6548979%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22GM's%20new%20EV%20charging%20hubs%20look%20exactly%20like%20gas%20stations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rendering%20of%20an%20EVgo%2FGM%20Energy-branded%20fast%20charging%20station%20with%20several%20pull-through%20stalls%20and%20a%20lit%20canopy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%