20or%20shift%20the%20group.%20With%20divorce%20or%20separation%2C%20the%20members%20may%20have%20to%20renegotiate%20their%20relationship%20not%20only%20to%20the%20partner%20that%20is%20separating%20but%20to%20the%20partner's%20friends%20or%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Hui%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friend's%20split%20can%20make%20us%20%26quot%3Bthink%20of%20our%20own%20relationship%20to%20divorce%2C%20changes%2C%20and%20endings%20in%20relationships%26quot%3B%20and%20bring%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-types-of-grief-what-they-mean-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeelings%20of%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sadness%2C%20anger%2C%20or%20betrayal.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20dealing%20with%20this%20grief%2C%20Hui%20says%20that%20%26quot%3Btaking%20time%20to%20understand%20how%20one%20has%20been%20impacted%20is%20a%20helpful%20opening%20in%20understanding%20the%20individual%2C%20nuanced%20process%20of%20addressing%20these%20difficult%20feelings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bdf5f1a9-e642-4464-ad41-d963c1b7a8ee%5C%22%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20move%20forward%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20Hui's%20advice%2C%20I%20ruminated%20on%20what%20exactly%20this%20divorce%20was%20bringing%20up%20for%20me.%20I%20felt%20secure%20in%20my%20own%20marriage%2C%20but%20couldn't%20deny%20that%20my%20friend's%20ex's%20entitled%20behavior%20over%20the%20years%20reminded%20me%20of%20my%20father%2C%20who%20had%20left%20my%20own%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20my%20experiences%20with%20them%20as%20a%20couple%20%E2%80%94%20vacations%2C%20dinner%20parties%2C%20game%20nights%20%E2%80%94%20that%20had%20felt%20like%20fond%20family%20memories%20now%20felt%20tainted%20and%20unsafe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20it's%20just%20that%20any%20loss%20of%20love%20hurts%3B%20public%20reaction%20to%20celebrity%20divorces%20certainly%20supports%20that%20theory.%20Their%20love%20had%20been%20a%20constant%20in%20my%20life.%20Now%20it's%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%2