0said%20that%20approximately%2075%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bdisengagement%26quot%3B%20problems%20has%20been%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%2C%20who%20is%20in%20Geneva%2C%20Switzerland%20for%20bilateral%20meetings%2C%20said%20this%20at%20an%20interactive%20session%20at%20the%20Global%20Centre%20for%20Security%20Policy%20-%20an%20independent%20think-tank.%20The%20minister%20further%20said%20that%20the%20bigger%20issue%20has%20been%20the%20increasing%20militarisation%20of%20the%20frontier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20clashes%20of%20June%202020%20affected%20the%20%26quot%3Bentirety%26quot%3B%20of%20India-China%20ties%2C%20asserting%20that%20%26quot%3BOne%20cannot%20have%20violence%20at%20the%20border%20and%20then%20say%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20relationship%20is%20insulated%20from%20it%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNegotiations%20are%20going%20on.%20We%20made%20some%20progress.%20I%20would%20say%20roughly%20you%20can%20say%20about%2075%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20disengagement%20problems%20are%20sorted%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3BWe%20still%20have%20some%20things%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20India%20and%20China%20have%20been%20at%20an%20all-time%20low%20as%20the%20militaries%20of%20both%20nations%20have%20been%20standing%20their%20ground%20since%20the%20standoff%20in%20Ladakh%20began%20in%20May%202020.%20The%20disengagement%20process%20began%20in%20February%202021%20and%20has%20been%20on%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoughly%2075%25%20of%20the%20disengagement%20problems%20with%20China%20has%20been%20sorted%20out%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20is%20scheduled%20to%20meet%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Wang%20Yi%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Switzerland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalks%20at%20both%20the%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20levels%20between%20India%20and%20China%20have%20held%20on%20an%20ongoing%20basis.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20that%20if%20there%20is%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20disengagement%20and%20there%20is%20a%20return%20to%20peace%20and%20tranquility%2C%20then%20we%20can%20look%20at%20other%20possibilities%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20partial%20disengagement%20from%20Galwan%2C%20Hot%20Springs%2C%20and%20Gogra%20happened%20in%20July%202020%20while%20full%20disengagement%20from%20Pangong%20Lake%20north%20and%20south%20banks%20took%20place%20in%20February%202021.%20However%2C%20Chinese%20soldiers%20are%20firmly%20entrenched%20in%20the%20Depsang%20Plains%20in%20northeastern%20Ladakh%20and%20show%20no%20signs%20of%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20or%20LAC%20between%20India%20and%20China%2C%20including%20China-occupied%20Tibet%2C%20is%20around%203%2C500%20km%20in%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20maintained%20that%20its%20ties%20with%20China%20cannot%20be%20normal%20unless%20there%20is%20peace%20in%20the%20border%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20basis%20obviously%20for%20a%20good%20relationship%2C%20I%20would%20say%20even%20for%20a%20normal%20relationship%2C%20was%20that%20there%20would%20be%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20in%20the%20border.%20After%20things%20started%20to%20take%20a%20better%20turn%20in%201988%2C%20we%20had%20a%20series%20of%20agreements%20which%20stabilised%20the%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVIOLATIONS%20BY%20CHINA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20how%20China%20unilaterally%20changed%20the%20status-quo%20along%20the%20LAC%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%20in%202020%20was%20in%20violation%20of%20multiple%20agreements%20for%20some%20reasons%20which%20are%20still%20entirely%20not%20clear%20to%20us%3B%20we%20can%20speculate%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Chinese%20actually%20moved%20a%20very%20large%20number%20of%20troops%20to%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20at%20the%20border%20and%20naturally%20in%20response%2C%20we%20moved%20our%20troops%20up.%20It%20was%20very%20difficult%20for%20us%20because%20we%20were%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20Covid%20lockdown%20at%20that%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20development%20as%20very%20dangerous%20and%20referring%20to%20the%20Glawan%20clashes%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%20we%20could%20see%20straight%20away%20that%20this%20was%20a%20very%20dangerous%20development%20because%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20large%20number%20of%20troops%20in%20these%20extreme%20heights%20and%20extreme%20cold%20in%20near%20proximity%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20mishap.%20And%20that's%20exactly%20what%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20now%20been%20negotiating%20close%20to%20four%20years%20and%20the%20first%20step%20of%20that%20is%20what%20we%20called%20disengagement%20which%20is%20their%20troops%20go%20back%20to%20their%20normal%20operating%20bases%20and%20our%20troops%20go%20back%20to%20their%20normal%20operating%20bases%20and%20where%20required%20we%20have%20an%20arrangement%20about%20patrolling%20because%20both%20of%20us%20patrol%20regularly%20in%20that%20border%20as%20I%20said%20it%20is%20not%20a%20legally%20delineated%20border.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIMPACT%20ON%20INDIA-CHINA%20TIES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20military%20clashes%20and%20subsequent%20standoff%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20China%20have%20been%20at%20an%20all-time%20low.%20The%20economic%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20have%20been%20imbalanced%20for%20the%20last%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20trade%20ties%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20the%20economic%20relationship%20with%20China%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bvery%20unfair%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunbalanced%26quot%3B.%20But%20he%20has%20maintained%20that%20India%20is%20not%20closed%20for%20business%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20ago%2C%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Germany%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20had%20said%20that%20India%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20closed%20to%20business%20from%20China%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20the%20issue%20is%20in%20which%20sectors%20the%20country%20does%20business%20with%20Beijing%20and%20on%20what%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20closed%20to%20business%20from%20China...I%20think%20the%20issue%20is%2C%20which%20sectors%20do%20you%20do%20business%20and%20what%20terms%20do%20you%20do%20business%3F%20It's%20far%20more%20complicated%20than%20a%20black%20and%20white%20binary%20answer%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Ladakh%20standoff%2C%20India%20has%20tightened%20its%20scrutiny%20of%20investments%20from%20Chinese%20companies%20and%20stopped%20all%20major%20projects%2C%20including%20in%20infrastructure.%20But%20as%20progress%20is%20made%20with%20China%20on%20disengagement%20along%20the%20LAC%2C%20government%20officials%2C%20including%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20have%20backed%20suggestions%20to%20allow%20more%20Chinese%20investment%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20investment%20scrutiny%2C%20India%20has%20also%20virtually%20blocked%20visas%20for%20all%20Chinese%20nationals%20since%202020%2C%20but%20is%20now%20considering%20easing%20them%20for%20Chinese%20technicians%2C%20as%20it%20had%20hindered%20investments%20worth%20billions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Ladakh%20standoff%2C%20passenger%20flights%20between%20India%20and%20China%20had%20also%20stopped%2C%20but%20with%20progress%20in%20disengagement%2C%20though%20slow%2C%20resumption%20of%20flights%20is%20now%20being%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20Aviation%20Minister%20Ram%20Mohan%20Naidu%20Kinjarapu%20said%20today%20that%20early%20resumption%20of%20direct%20flights%20between%20India%20and%20China%20have%20been%20discuss