al%20media%2C%20was%20arrested%20and%20later%20confessed%20to%20the%20crime.%20The%20federal%20court%20in%20Lausanne%20rejected%20his%20appeal%20for%20release%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20Warning%3A%20Disturbing%20content%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20autopsy%20determined%20that%20Ms%C2%A0Joksimovic%20was%20strangled%20before%20her%20death%2C%20a%20detail%20corroborated%20by%20Thomas%20in%20his%20confession.%20Her%20body%20was%20dismembered%20in%20the%20laundry%20room%20using%20a%20jigsaw%2C%20knife%2C%20and%20garden%20shears.%20According%20to%20local%20media%20outlet%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bzbasel.ch%2Fbasel%2Fbaselland%2Fbundesgericht-mord-in-binningen-ehemann-soll-die-leiche-seiner-frau-verstuemmelt-haben-ld.2668305%5C%22%3EBasel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20some%20of%20her%20remains%20were%20later%20chopped%20with%20a%20hand%20blender%2C%20%26quot%3Bpureed%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20dissolved%20in%20a%20chemical%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThomas%20claims%20that%20he%20killed%20his%20wife%20in%20self-defence%2C%20stating%20that%20she%20attacked%20him%20with%20a%20knife.%20After%20the%20murder%2C%20he%20reportedly%20panicked%20and%20proceeded%20to%20dismember%20her%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20medical-forensic%20reports%20contradict%20Thomas's%20self-defence%20claim.%20Investigators%20have%20found%20%26quot%3Bconcrete%20indications%20of%20a%20mental%20illness%26quot%3B%20in%20Thomas%20and%20described%20him%20as%20having%20%26quot%3Bsadistic%20tendencies.%26quot%3B%20They%20noted%20his%20%26quot%3Bremarkably%20high%20level%20of%20criminal%20energy%2C%20lack%20of%20empathy%2C%20and%20cold-bloodedness%26quot%3B%20following%20the%20murder%20of%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20also%20disclosed%20that%20Thomas%20had%20previously%20strangled%20his%20wife.%20Additionally%2C%20a%20former%20partner%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20once%20grabbed%20the%20beauty%20queen%20