etterindia.com%2F359581%2Finspiring-senior-citizens-india-running-successful-startups-isro-restaurants-oil-business-daycares%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome-cooked%20specialties%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20across%20the%20country.%20From%20Uma%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20prawn%20pickles%20in%20Kerala%20to%20Bhavana%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Enankhatais%20%3C%2Fem%3E(biscuits)%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Annie%20Philip%E2%80%99s%20matured%20plum%20cake%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Tocco%20is%20a%20melting%20pot%20of%20regional%20delicacies!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20women%20can%20be%20found%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20you%20just%20need%20to%20look%20and%20spend%20a%20few%20minutes%20talking%20to%20them.%20Ask%20your%20mother%20or%20aunt%20about%20their%20wishes%2C%20and%20if%20they%20are%20anything%20like%20Bhavana%20or%20Uma%2C%20they%20would%20have%20definitely%20harboured%20dreams%20of%20creating%20their%20own%20identity%20through%20cooking.%20Tocco%20makes%20it%20easy%20for%20neighbourhood%20home%20chefs%20to%20do%20just%20that%2C%20without%20the%20hassle%20of%20branding%20or%20marketing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20for%20this%20platform%20was%20born%20from%20founder%20Reshma%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20own%20desire%20to%20experience%20the%20taste%20of%20home%20while%20living%20away.%20After%20moving%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20work%2C%20she%20found%20herself%20caught%20in%20the%20cycle%20of%20eating%20outside%2C%20always%20craving%20her%20%3Cem%3Eamma%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20tasty%20food.%20Realising%20she%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20one%20looking%20for%20authentic%20Kerala%20food%2C%20she%20started%20making%20banana%20chips%20and%20selling%20them%20through%20her%20brand%2C%20%E2%80%98MeenGurry%20Memories%E2%80%99%2C%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPacking%20memories%20of%20her%20%3Cem%3Eamma%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Eammamma%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmother%E2%80%99s)%20generations-old%20recipe%20for%20the%20perfect%2C%20thin%2C%20and%20crispy%20banana%20chips%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20game-changer%20for%20Reshma%2C%20who%20was%20then%20working%20at%20an%20AI%2Fhealthcare%20startup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tocco%20chef%20Annie%20baking%20a%20plum%20cake.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-150x200.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828.jpeg%20960w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365472%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETocco%20chef%20Annie%20baking%20a%20plum%20cake.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20passion%20project%20soon%20took%20on%20a%20life%20of%20its%20own%20when%20she%20introduced%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20prawn%20and%20mango%20pickle.%20Rather%20than%20making%20the%20food%20herself%2C%20Reshma%20decided%20to%20create%20a%20platform%20where%20people%20like%20her%20mother%20and%20aunt%20could%20sell%20their%20dishes%20directly.%20This%20would%20help%20them%20become%20financially%2